JSON (JavaScript Object Notation) < http://json.org ( #http://json.org ) > is a subset of JavaScript syntax (ECMA-262 3rd edition) used as a lightweight data interchange format.

json ( #json ) exposes an API familiar to users of the standard library marshal ( #marshal ) and pickle ( #pickle ) modules.
